<h2>Cultural Memory in Contemporary Narrative (Promotionsprojekt)</h2>
<h3>Andrea Camilleri’s Montalbano Series</h3>
<hr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h4>Allgemeine Angaben</h4>
<dl class='attribute_listing'>
